snippet.title: What Meghan Markle Was Really Like Before The Fame
snippet.description:
We all love fairy tales in which a common woman gets swept away by a Prince and soon becomes a part of royalty herself. It’s a tale as old as time they say.

In today’s modern world, the British royal family saw that story play out when Meghan Markle and Prince Harry began dating and eventually tied the knot. Meghan went from a fairly unknown actress to becoming the Duchess of Sussex.

So, what was Meghan’s life like before she became part of royalty? Did she go through struggles like all us commoners go through? To find out, watch this video!
